<h3 id="dp"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">DP</code></h3>

<p>Select <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">DP</code> input when you are using the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">DP</code> connector.</p>

<h3 id="hdmi-1--hdmi-2"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">HDMI 1</code> / <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">HDMI 2</code></h3>

<p>Select <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">HDMI 1</code> or <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">HDMI 2</code> input when you are using the HMDI connector.</p>

<h3 id="auto-select"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Auto Select</code></h3>

<p>Allow the monitor to automatically scan for available input sources.</p>

